@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Posts";
    Layout = null;
}
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>EduSys — Posts</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/css/geral.css" />
    <style>
        body { background: linear-gradient(165deg, #051211 0%, #0B2B28 50%, #051211 100%); }

        .posts-page { min-height: 100vh; display: flex; flex-direction: column; }

        /* Topbar */
        .posts-topbar {
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 10;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 16px;
            padding: 14px 32px;
            background: rgba(5,18,17,0.85);
            backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
        }

        .back-link {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 7px;
            font-family: var(--font-mono);
            font-size: 10px;
            letter-spacing: 0.14em;
            color: var(--text-600);
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: color 0.2s;
        }
        .back-link:hover { color: var(--lime-300); }
        .back-link svg { width: 14px; height: 14px; }

        .posts-topbar-sep { width: 1px; height: 18px; background: var(--border); }

        .posts-page-title {
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--text-100);
            letter-spacing: 0.04em;
        }
        .posts-page-title span { color: var(--lime-400); }

        /* Content */
        .posts-content {
            flex: 1;
            padding: 36px 32px;
            max-width: 860px;
            width: 100%;
            margin: 0 auto;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        /* Header de seção */
        .posts-header {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-bottom: 28px;
        }

        .posts-count {
            font-family: var(--font-mono);
            font-size: 10px;
            letter-spacing: 0.15em;
            color: var(--text-600);
        }

        /* Post card */
        .post-card {
            background: var(--bg-card);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
            padding: 22px 24px;
            margin-bottom: 14px;
            backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
            transition: border-color 0.22s, box-shadow 0.22s, transform 0.22s;
        }
        .post-card:hover {
            border-color: var(--border-strong);
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
            transform: translateY(-1px);
        }

        .post-header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: flex-start;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            gap: 12px;
        }

        .post-title {
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--text-100);
            line-height: 1.3;
        }

        .post-date {
            font-family: var(--font-mono);
            font-size: 9px;
            letter-spacing: 0.12em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: var(--text-600);
            padding: 4px 10px;
            background: var(--bg-row);
            border-radius: var(--radius-full);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            white-space: nowrap;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        .post-body {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: var(--text-400);
            line-height: 1.72;
            margin-bottom: 18px;
        }

        .post-actions {
            display: flex;
            gap: 8px;
            padding-top: 14px;
            border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
        }

        .post-btn {
            font-family: var(--font-mono);
            font-size: 10px;
            letter-spacing: 0.14em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            padding: 8px 16px;
            border-radius: var(--radius-md);
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.2s;
        }

        .post-btn-primary {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #76C057 0%, #3C8F40 100%);
            color: #0D2B18;
            font-weight: 700;
            border: 1px solid rgba(118,192,87,0.25);
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(118,192,87,0.15);
        }
        .post-btn-primary:hover {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #A8D582 0%, #76C057 100%);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(118,192,87,0.28);
        }

        .post-btn-secondary {
            background: transparent;
            color: var(--text-600);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
        }
        .post-btn-secondary:hover {
            border-color: var(--border-strong);
            color: var(--text-200);
            background: rgba(74,139,130,0.07);
        }

        /* Glow */
        .glow-posts-tr {
            width: 450px; height: 400px;
            top: -80px; right: -60px;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(118,192,87,0.06) 0%, transparent 70%);
        }
        .glow-posts-bl {
            width: 400px; height: 400px;
            bottom: -80px; left: -60px;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(74,139,130,0.06) 0%, transparent 70%);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="posts-page">

    <div class="glow-blob glow-posts-tr"></div>
    <div class="glow-blob glow-posts-bl"></div>

    <!-- Topbar -->
    <header class="posts-topbar">
        <a class="back-link" asp-controller="Aluno" asp-action="Index">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path d="M19 12H5M12 19l-7-7 7-7"/>
            </svg>
            Dashboard
        </a>
        <div class="posts-topbar-sep"></div>
        <div class="navbar-brand">
            <div class="navbar-logo-icon">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 18 18" fill="none">
                    <rect x="1" y="1" width="6" height="6" rx="1" stroke="#76C057" stroke-width="1.5"/>
                    <rect x="11" y="1" width="6" height="6" rx="1" stroke="#76C057" stroke-width="1.5"/>
                    <rect x="1" y="11" width="6" height="6" rx="1" stroke="#76C057" stroke-width="1.5"/>
                    <rect x="11" y="11" width="6" height="6" rx="1" stroke="#A8D582" stroke-width="1.5" opacity=".55"/>
                </svg>
            </div>
            <span class="navbar-brand-text" style="font-size:13px;">EDU<span>SYS</span></span>
        </div>
        <div class="posts-topbar-sep"></div>
        <p class="posts-page-title">POSTS<span>.</span></p>
        <div style="margin-left:auto;">
            <button class="btn btn-primary" style="padding:8px 18px;font-size:10px;">+ Novo Post</button>
        </div>
    </header>

    <!-- Content -->
    <main class="posts-content anim-1">

        <div class="posts-header">
            <div>
                <h2 style="font-size:20px;font-weight:700;color:var(--text-100);">Suas Publicações</h2>
                <p style="font-size:12px;color:var(--text-600);margin-top:3px;">Anotações, dúvidas e projetos compartilhados</p>
            </div>
            <span class="posts-count">3 POSTS</span>
        </div>

        <!-- Post 1 -->
        <article class="post-card">
            <div class="post-header">
                <h3 class="post-title">Dúvida sobre P2 de Compiladores</h3>
                <span class="post-date">HOJE</span>
            </div>
            <p class="post-body">
                Alguém pode me ajudar a entender o algoritmo de análise sintática LL(1)?
                Estou com dificuldade nas tabelas de parsing e não consigo entender como construir
                os conjuntos First e Follow corretamente.
            </p>
            <div class="post-actions">
                <button class="post-btn post-btn-primary">Ver mais</button>
                <button class="post-btn post-btn-secondary">Comentar</button>
            </div>
        </article>

        <!-- Post 2 -->
        <article class="post-card">
            <div class="post-header">
                <h3 class="post-title">Anotações — Banco de Dados II</h3>
                <span class="post-date">ONTEM</span>
            </div>
            <p class="post-body">
                Notas da aula de hoje sobre normalização: 1NF (atomicidade dos valores),
                2NF (remove dependências parciais), 3NF (remove dependências transitivas).
                Lembrete: sempre normalize até pelo menos 3NF para garantir integridade dos dados!
            </p>
            <div class="post-actions">
                <button class="post-btn post-btn-primary">Ver mais</button>
                <button class="post-btn post-btn-secondary">Comentar</button>
            </div>
        </article>

        <!-- Post 3 -->
        <article class="post-card">
            <div class="post-header">
                <h3 class="post-title">Projeto Final — Ideia</h3>
                <span class="post-date">22/03</span>
            </div>
            <p class="post-body">
                Pensando em desenvolver um sistema de gestão acadêmica para o projeto final.
                Stack planejada: ASP.NET MVC + C# + SQL Server.
                Quem quiser participar, pode me procurar!
            </p>
            <div class="post-actions">
                <button class="post-btn post-btn-primary">Ver mais</button>
                <button class="post-btn post-btn-secondary">Comentar</button>
            </div>
        </article>

    </main>
</div>
</body>
</html>
